short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Free Resume Builder, Job Search & Contacts Tracker

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Put your hiring journey on autopilot. Save Jobs, Contacts, Companies & Resumes in one place.

SkillMil is an AI powered All-in-One Hiring, Job Searching, and Personalized Career Development Platform. The Chrome extension works with multiple job boards, and simplifies the search to find the perfect match. Whether you're a job seeker or employer, you'll never lose your place in your hiring or recruiting journey again!

JOB SEEKERS & VETERANS
Try our FREE resume builder!

Learn more: 
https://www.skillmil.com/resume-builder
https://www.skillmil.com/veteran-resume-builder

Get Started:
https://signup.skillmil.com/signup


✧ ✧ KEY BENEFITS ✧ ✧

✓  Organize job search & candidate profiles in one place
✓  Bookmark job postings, candidates & contacts from Linkedin, Indeed, 
     ZipRecruiter and more to come!
✓  Utilize AI to maximize job searches and create ATS ready resumes 
✓  Save full LinkedIn profiles for future research and grow your 
     professional pipeline & network. 
✓  Save notes on each contact or job opening.
✓  Share your progress with your team, career advisor, family or friend. 
     SkillMil lets you collaborate and share your progress to help you stay 
     on track. 
✓  Keep your place in the hiring and recruiting journey!

✧ ✧ POWERFUL AI TOOLS✧ ✧

✓   Milly™ - an interactive resume builder & job description tool
✓   SkillScore - Matching your abilities to job postings with precision. 
✓   VMET Parser - VETERANS! Simply upload your VMET (Verification of 
      Military Experience & Training) to translate your military skills for a 
      personalized resume profile
✓   Compliance ready profiles for smoother WOTC certification

RECRUITING SOLUTIONS & PRICING PLANS
https://www.skillmil.com/recruiting-solutions

PRIVACY & SECURITY 
At SkillMil we are committed to protecting your privacy. The information we gather or process is used strictly to enrich and speed up your hiring journey. Your information is not and has not been sold to third parties. More information on privacy and security can be found on our website here: 

https://www.skillmil.com/privacy-policy 
https://www.skillmil.com/terms-conditions
